00:22.587 --> 00:22.761
they're not
going to survive him.

00:23.849 --> 00:24.372
- What can we do?
- Take a road trip

00:25.112 --> 00:26.069
to Vegas to kill my dad.

00:32.597 --> 00:35.600
[tense music]

00:35.644 --> 00:38.560
♪

00:38.603 --> 00:40.736
- Forgotten all
human etiquette.

00:40.779 --> 00:42.738
What's expected of me here?

00:42.781 --> 00:44.914
Just be cool, be normal.

00:44.957 --> 00:47.482
What do I do with my eyes--
look at him, the floor?

00:47.525 --> 00:50.572
Stop! Trying to hide the
tension only makes it obvious.

00:50.615 --> 00:53.792
Fuck, where am I?
I should know that.

00:53.836 --> 00:55.577
Okay, piece it together--
two 8-balls of coke.

00:55.620 --> 00:57.622
Saya wouldn't shut up
about water skiing.

00:57.666 --> 00:59.668
