but that wasn't it.

00:59.711 --> 01:01.148
No, none of that matters.

01:01.191 --> 01:02.540
Nothing before
the acid matter.

01:02.584 --> 01:04.238
Numbness in the face
and hands.

01:04.281 --> 01:06.240
Stomach lurches,
compressing in on itself.

01:06.283 --> 01:08.329
