they are just the best liars.

02:10.739 --> 02:12.654
- It gives people a reason
not to act like assholes.

02:12.697 --> 02:14.699
- [scoffs]
You're an asshole.

02:14.743 --> 02:16.745
- I am the most well adjusted
person in this car.

02:16.788 --> 02:19.661
